        token - the current token for the parser
        parser - the parser
        parseFieldMatcher - the ParseFieldMatcher to use to match field names
        otherOptions - a Map of options to be populated by successive calls to this method which will then be passed to the AbstractValuesSourceParser.createFactory(String, ValuesSourceType, ValueType, Map) method
        Returns:
        true if the current token was correctly parsed, false otherwise

        java.io.IOException - if an error occurs whilst parsing
